description: Vicki and Jeana have made a pact to get in shape, but getting up at 5:30 a.m. every morning may prove to be the bigger challenge. Vicki likes her big home in Coto and struggles with the notion that downsizing equals failure. Since the death of Lou Knickerbocker, Tammy has tried to be a supportive mother to her daughters.
